title: Porter Bibb Says CBS' David Rhodes Could Succeed Ailes (Audio)

description:
(Bloomberg) -- Taking Stock with Kathleen Hays and Pimm Fox. GUEST: Media and entertainment guru Porter Bibb of Mediatech Capital Partners, on Roger Ailes' resignation from Fox News, and what will happen with the network's top talent.
